data.description: Welcome! You won’t believe the space in this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom four level split-home centrally located in Coon Rapids. The thoughtfully designed layout offers flexibility, with a family room featuring a wood-burning fireplace for a warm and cozy ambiance. Vaulted ceilings contribute to an open and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen has a center island, ample cabinet space, and a deck accessible through sliding doors, extending the living space outdoors. The expansive backyard provides opportunities for gardening, play, or relaxation. This home has been well lived in by a large family, and presents a wonderful opportunity for its new owners!
